uot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">50,00,000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:126px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">25,00,000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n', 'Water (Prevention and Control of Pollution) Act, 1974 and Air (Prevention and Control of Pollution) Act, 1974', '', 0, '<ol>\n	<li><span><span><span><strong><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Application</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>The Proponent shall submit Application on-line through the SWAAGAT portal. (swaagat.tripura.gov.in) </span></span></span></span></li>\n		<li><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>The applications must be filled as per instructions and submitted with the required documents. </span></span></span></span></li>\n		<li><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>When the application is filled up and submitted, a message/ e-mail will be sent to scrutiny officer. </span></span></span></span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n	<li><span><span><span><strong><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Processing of the Application</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span>\n\n	<ol>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>The application would be scrutinized by the scrutiny officer and if any query raised by Scrutiny officer then the applicant would be required to address the query.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Subsequently, if the application is found to be in order and all the attached documents is meeting requirements the application would move to Approval authority</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ol>', '<p><span><span><span><strong><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Consent to Establish (Fresh/Proposed)</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li>\n	<ol>\n		<li>\n		<ol>\n			<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Land Documents/ Land Diversion/ Agreement Paper/ Parcha etc. </span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n			<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>No Objection Certificate from neighbours and land owner.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n			<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Site Plan of the unit.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n			<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Detail project Report including cost of Capital Investment (item-wise); land, building, manufacturing process, pollution control devices like ETP, STP, soak pit, stack of DG, boiler, furnace, heat emission etc.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n			<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Consent fees (Net Banking, Debit card, NEFT/RTGS).</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n			<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Environmental Clearance (in case of B1 and B2 category projects).</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n		</ol>\n		</li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ol>', '<p><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>21 days</span></span></span> </span></span></span></p>'),
(23, '<a href=\"/node/38205\" hreflang=\"en\">TIDC-Water</a>', '', 0, '', 'Special Services', 'Tripura Industrial Development Corporation Limited', '<ul>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Rs. 10/- per KL per Month  ( if Supplied by TIDC  )</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Rs. 2/- per KL per  Month ( If arranged by the Industrial Unit) </span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>', 'Water Connection', '', 0, '<p><span><span><strong><span><span><span>A. Application for Water Connection :</span></span></span></strong></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>The Applicant  shall submit Application for water connection  on-line through  SWAAGAT portal</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>(www.swaagat.tripura.gov.in)</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>The  application contain the mode of water requirement  i.e. whether required from TIDC or arrange by </span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>the unit itself . </span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>No user charges required for submission of Application.  </span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>The application is then be  scrutinized online and any discrepancies in the application will be  </span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>       communicated   to   the applicant </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p>B. <span><span><span><span><strong><span><span><span>Processing of the Application</span></span></span></strong><strong><span><span><span>:</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>The submitted complete application is then be  checked for the quantity  of  water required   and also </span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span>        verify documents submitted by the applicant. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n	<li><span><span><span><span>Joint field visit by the team consisting of Junior Engineer &amp; Pump Operator of the concerned Industrial </span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span>            Estate and the applicant is then be carried out to assess the actual quantity of water may be supplied to      the Industrial unit. </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n	<li><span><span><span><span> After assessment , the application is then be  sent to the Managing Director, TIDC Ltd with </span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span>        recommendation and Managing Director will take decision for approval or rejection.</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol start=\"4\">\n	<li><span><span><span><span>Once approved by the Managing Director, consent letter for water connection  shall be issued to the </span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span>      Applicant.</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol start=\"5\">\n	<li><span><span><span><span>After getting consent letter from TIDC Ltd,  industrial unit can take initiative to set up their own water </span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span>       arrangement by installing submersible pump, tube well or any other arrangement in case of own        arrangement. </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ol start=\"6\">\n	<li><span><span><span><span>If TIDC provide the   water connection, it may take at least  7( Seven) days to provide the water </span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span>       connection . </span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>', '<ul>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>In case of own arrangement: The applicant has to submit self declaration mentioning </span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span> information like the details of boring with capacity, Pump discharge head/hr., dia of boring etc.   </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>In case of own arrangement: The applicant has to submit self declaration mentioning </span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>actual quantity of water required per day in KL. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>', '<p><span><span><span><span>10 ( Ten) days<strong> </strong></span></span></span></span></p>');
INSERT INTO `information_wizards` (`id`, `title`, `field_fee_structure_files`, `delta`, `field_noc_master_link`, `field_wizard_category`, `field_wizard_department`, `field_wizard_fee_text`, `field_wizard_noc_name`, `field_wizard_notification`, `delta_1`, `field_wizard_process`, `field_wizard_required_documents`, `field_wizard_timeline`) VALUES
