lor:#333333\">Rs.7.00 Lakh per Shed </span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:170px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Dukli Industrial Area </span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:123px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Rs.8,000/- per Acre </span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:123px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Rs.7.00 Lakh per Acre </span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:123px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Rs.11,000/- per shed </span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px sol