e=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:123px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Nil</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:123px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Nil </span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:123px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Rs.5.00 Per Sq.Ft. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:113px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:#333333\">Rs.50.00 Per Sq.Ft. </span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n', 'Industrial Land Allotment', '', 0, '<p><span><span><span><span><strong><span><span><span>A. </span></span></span></strong><strong><span><span><span>Application for Land Allotment:</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>The Applicant  shall submit Application on-line through SWAAGAT portal (www.swaagat.tripura.gov.in)</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>The application must be filled in complete form and all required documents must be uploaded. The applicant must also deposit the user charges along with the application. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>The application is then scrutinized online and any discrepancies in the application is communicated to the  Applicant </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><strong><span><span><span>B.  </span></span></span></strong><strong><span><span><span>Processing of the Application:</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>The submitted complete application is then checked for the size of the land or Size of the shed or  no. of Shed  to be allotted and also verify  documents submitted by the applicant. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>Joint Field visit by the team consisting of Junior Engineer of the concerned Industrial Estate and the applicant is then be carried out for identification  of the land to be allotted. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>After identification of land, the application is then sent to the Managing Director, TIDC Ltd with recommendation and Managing Director will take decision for approval or rejection.  </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>Once approved by the Managing Director, consent letter for Allotment shall be issued to the Applicant. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>The Consent letter will also contain the amount of   Non-refundable premium &amp; Advance Rent and the Applicant must pay the required amount. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>After successful receipt of the payment, the allotment order will be issued on lease basis for 30 years with a condition that possession of the land/Shed will be given only after execution of lease deed agreement. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>The execution and registration agreement for lease of land /shed shall then be executed within 3(Three) months from the date of issuance of Allotment Order.  </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>After completion of above points this the Physical possession of the land will be given. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>', '<ol>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Proprietorship Firm:-</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Detailed Project Report along with justification of land requirement and Process Flow Chart.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Concept of Solid Waste/Liquid Waste/Effluent Generation shall be detailed in the Project Report with planning of treatment. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Identity Proof of the applicant (Adhaar Car/Voter ID/ Driving License/International Passport/ Bank Pass Book)</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Address Proof ( Current telephone bill/ Current Telephone Bill)</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Partnership  Firm :-</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Detailed Project Report along with justification of land requirement and Process Flow Chart</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Concept of Solid Waste/Liquid Waste/Effluent Generation shall be detailed in the Project Report with planning of treatment. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Identity Proof of the each partner  (Adhaar Car/Voter ID/ Driving License/International Passport/ Bank Pass Book)</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Address Proof of the each partner( Current telephone bill/ Current Telephone Bill)</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Certified copy of firm registration certificate </span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Copy of partnership deed.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<ol start=\"3\">\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Cooperative Society :-</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Detailed Project Report along with justification of land requirement and Process Flow Chart</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Concept of Solid Waste/Liquid Waste/Effluent Generation shall be detailed in the Project Report with planning of treatment. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>Identity Proof of the each member of society (Adhaar Car/Voter ID/ Driving  License/International Passport/ Bank Pass Book).</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>Address Proof of the each member ( Current telephone bill/ Current Telephone Bill</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>Certified copy of the Registration of Society and its By-Law.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<ol start=\"4\">\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Private Limited Company :- </span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Detailed Project Report along with justification of land requirement and Process Flow Chart</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Concept of Solid Waste/Liquid Waste/Effluent Generation shall be detailed in the Project Report with planning of treatment. </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Identity Proof of the each Director of Company (Adhaar Car/Voter ID/ Driving          License/International Passport/ Bank Pass Book).</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Address Proof of the each Director  ( Current telephone bill/ Current Telephone Bill</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span><span><span>Company Incorporation Certificate. </span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ul>', '<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>Land Allotment: 14 days.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>'),
(25, '<a href=\"/node/39410\" hreflang=\"en\">Urban - Trade License</a>', '', 0, '', 'Special Services', 'Urban Development Department', '', 'Trade License', '', 0, '<ol>\n	<li><span><span><span><strong><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Application</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>The Proponent shall submit Application on-line </span></span></span></span></li>\n		<li><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>The applications must be filled as per instructions and submitted with the required documents. </span></span></span></span></li>\n		<li><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>When the application is filled up and submitted, a message/ e-mail will be sent to scrutiny officer. </span></span></span></span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<ol start=\"2\">\n	<li><span><span><span><strong><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Processing of the Application</span></span></span></strong></span></span></span>\n\n	<ol>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>The application would be scrutinized by the scrutiny officer and if any query raised by Scrutiny officer then the applicant would be required to address the query.</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Subsequently, if the application is found to be in order and all the attached documents is meeting requirements the application would move to Approval authority</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ol>', '<ol>\n	<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>For ordinary Trade license</span></span></span></span></span></span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Voter card or Aadhar card</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>For partnership trade license</span></span></span></span></span></span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Partnership deed</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Proof of all partner</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>For financial business</span></span></span></span></span></span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>RBI certificate</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>PAN card</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n	<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>For insurance Business</span></span></span></span></span></span>\n	<ol>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>IRDA document</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>PAN card</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ol>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<ol start=\"5\">\n	<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>For company business</span></span></span></span></span></span>\n\n	<ol>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Company Act 1956 documents</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n		<li><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>PAN card</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>\n	</ol>\n	</li>\n</ol>', '<p><span><span><span>Registration - 7 days</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>Renewal- Auto on payment of fees</span></span></span><strong> </strong></p>');
INSERT INTO `information_wizards` (`id`, `title`, `field_fee_structure_files`, `delta`, `field_noc_master_link`, `field_wizard_category`, `field_wizard_department`, `field_wizard_fee_text`, `field_wizard_noc_name`, `field_wizard_notification`, `delta_1`, `field_wizard_process`, `field_wizard_required_documents`, `field_wizard_timeline`) VALUES
(26, '<a href=\"/node/441279\" hreflang=\"en\">L06 - Boiler Manufactures Registration</a>', '', 0, '', 'Other Services', 'Boilers Organisation', '<p><strong><span><span><span>Fee for Boiler Manufacturers: </span></span></span></strong><span><span><span>Nil</span></span></span></p>\n\n<div class=\"flow-chart\">\n<h3>Flow Chart of Stagewise Details with Cost and Time:</h3>\n\n<h4>Registration of Boilers Manufacturers under the Boilers Act, 1923</h4>\n\n<table border=\"1\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"margin-left:37px; border-collapse:collapse; border:1px solid\" width=\"100%\">\n	<thead>\n		<tr>\n			<th>Sl.</th>\n			<th>Stage</th>\n			<th>Timeline</th>\n			<th>Cost</th>\n		</tr>\n	</thead>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>1.</td>\n			<td>Application submission by applicant</td>\n			<td>0 Day</td>\n			<td>Nil</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>2.</td>\n			<td>Chief Inspector of Factories &amp; Boilers</td>\n			<td>30 Days</td>\n			<td>---</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td class=\"total\" colspan=\"2\">Total</td>\n			<td>30 Days</td>\n			<td> </td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:8px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b>G. <u>Risk category</u>: </b>All boilers are in high Risk category and documents needed as mentioned in 1(c).</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b>H. <u>Size of Firm</u>: </b>All boilers and documents needed as mentioned in 1(c).</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; margin-bottom:13px\"> </p>\n\n<p><strong>I. Business Location:</strong></p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"margin-left:37px; border-collapse:collapse; border:1px solid\" width=\"100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Business Location</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Industrial Estate</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Urban</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Rural</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Documents to be submitted with the Application as per Sl. No.1(C)</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Applicable for all Business Locations</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Applicable for all Business Locations</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Applicable for all Business Locations</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>J. Investor:</strong></p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"margin-left:37px; border-collapse:collapse; border:1px solid\" width=\"100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Investor</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Domestic Investor</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Foreign Investor</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Documents to be submitted with the Application as per Sl. No.1(C)</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Documents as per Sl. No.1(C)</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Documents as per Sl. No.1(C) and permission from the authority of Govt. of India</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n', 'Application for Registration of Boilers Manufactures under the Boilers Act, 1923', '', 0, '<p><strong>Application for Registration of Boilers Manufactures underthe Boilers Act, 1923:</strong></p>\n\n<p><strong>   A.Procedure/Processing for submission of online application:</strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>The Entrepreneur shall submit application on-line through <strong>SWAAGAT </strong>(<a href=\"https://swaagat.tripura.gov.in\">https://swaagat.tripura.gov.in</a>).</li>\n	<li>The online application, to be verified whether all required documents are attached with fee details.</li>\n	<li>The deficiencies, if any, in the application, shall be informed to the applicant.</li>\n</ul>', '<ol>\n	<li><strong>Checklist of Documents to be submitted with the Application</strong><strong>:</strong></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p>               • Workshop Ownership (or) Lease Agreement.</p>\n\n<p>               • List of the Machinery, Tools and Equipment.</p>\n\n<p>               • List of Testing Facilities.</p>\n\n<p>    • List of Technical Personnel with their designation, qualifications andexperience along with their certificates.</p>\n\n<p>               • List of welders employed along with their copies of current certificates.</p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Citizenship Certificate or Permanent Resident Certificate.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>• PAN card.</p>\n\n<p>• Aadhaar card.</p>\n\n<p>• Passport size photograph with signature.</p>', '<p>• Registration of Boiler Manufacturer: 30 days.</p>');
INSERT INTO `information_wizards` (`id`, `title`, `field_fee_structure_files`, `delta`, `field_noc_master_link`, `field_wizard_category`, `field_wizard_department`, `field_wizard_fee_text`, `field_wizard_noc_name`, `field_wizard_notification`, `delta_1`, `field_wizard_process`, `field_wizard_required_documents`, `field_wizard_timeline`) VALUES
(27, '<a href=\"/node/38220\" hreflang=\"en\">L05 - Boiler Renewal</a>', '', 0, '<a href=\"/node/30085\" hreflang=\"en\">OTH-FB1</a>', 'Renewal', 'Boilers Organisation', '<div class=\"flow-chart\">\n<h3>Flow Chart of Stagewise Details with Cost and Time:</h3>\n\n<h4>Renewal of Boiler License under the Boilers Act, 1923</h4>\n\n<table border=\"1\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" width=\"100%\">\n	<thead>\n		<tr>\n			<th>Sl.</th>\n			<th>Stage</th>\n			<th>Timeline</th>\n			<th>Cost</th>\n		</tr>\n	</thead>\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td>1.</td>\n			<td>Application submission by applicant</td>\n			<td>0 Day</td>\n			<td>Fee as per IBR, 1950, as notified from time to time.</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td>2.</td>\n			<td>Chief Inspector of Factories &amp; Boilers</td>\n			<td>7 Days</td>\n			<td>---</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td class=\"total\" colspan=\"2\">Total</td>\n			<td>7 Days</td>\n			<td> </td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n</div>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"tab-stops:163.5pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><b><u><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif\">Registration &amp; Renewal Fee for Boilers</span></span></span></u></b><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif\">:</span></span></span></b></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:30px; text-align:center\"> </p>\n\n<ol>\n	<li align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:17px; text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"tab-stops:163.5pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif\">Registration Fee for Boilers </span></span></span></b></span></span></span></span></li>\n</ol>\n\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"margin-left:97px; text-align:center; margin-bottom:13px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"tab-stops:163.5pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><b><span style=\"font-size:13.5pt\"><span style=\"line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif\">[Regulation 385].</span></span></span></b></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<table align=\"center\" border=\"1\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" style=\"\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:49px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">SL. No. </span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:498px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Boiler Rating</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:91px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Fee in Rupees</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:49px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">(1)</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:498px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">(2)</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:91px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">(3)</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:49px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">1</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:498px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">For Small Industrial Boiler as per chapter XIV</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:91px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">1200</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:49px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">2</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:498px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">For Boiler Rating not exceeding 10 sq. meters</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:91px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">1800</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:49px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">3</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:498px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-he