:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">20400</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:49px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">22</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:498px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">For Boilers Rating exceeding 2800 sq. meters but not exceeding 3000 sq. meters </span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:91px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:150%\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">21600</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; text-indent:36.0pt; margin-bottom:13px\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; text-indent:36.0pt; margin-bottom:13px\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; text-indent:36.0pt; margin-bottom:13px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">Above 3000 sq. meters, for every 200 sq. meters or part thereof, an additional fee of Rs. 600 shall be charged.</span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align:justify; text-indent:36.0pt; margin-bottom:13px\"><s