n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:144px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\">1,000/-</span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; margin-bottom:13px\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:8px\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:8px\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-bottom:8px\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b>G. <u>Risk category</u>: </b>All boilers are in high Risk category and documents needed as mentioned in 1(c).</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:107%\"><span style=\"font-family:Calibri,sans-serif\"><b>H. <u>Size of Firm</u>: </b>All boilers and documents needed as mentioned in 1(c).</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; margin-bottom:13px\"> </p>\n\n<p style=\"margin-left:30px; margin-bottom:13px\"> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>I. Business Location:</strong></p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" width=\"100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Business Location</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Industrial Estate</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Urban</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Rural</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Documents to be submitted with the Application as per Sl. No.1(C)</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Applicable for all Business Locations</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Applicable for all Business Locations</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Applicable for all Business Locations</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p><strong>J. Investor:</strong></p>\n\n<table border=\"1\" class=\"MsoTableGrid\" width=\"100%\">\n	<tbody>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Investor</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Domestic Investor</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:1px solid black; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><b><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Foreign Investor</span></b></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Documents to be submitted with the Application as per Sl. No.1(C)</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Documents as per Sl. No.1(C)</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:250px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,serif\">Documents as per Sl. No.1(C) and permission from the authority of Govt. of India</span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n', 'Application for Renewal of Boilers under the Boilers Act, 1923', '', 0, '<p><strong>Submission of Application: </strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>The Entrepreneur shall submit application on-line through <strong>SWAAGAT </strong> (<a href=\"https://swaagat.tripura.gov.in\">https://swaagat.tripura.gov.in</a>).</li>\n	<li>The online application, to be verified whether all required documents are attached with fee details.</li>\n	<li>The deficiencies, if any, in the application, shall be informed to the applicant.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Processing of the Application: </strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>If the application is found to be in order, the department will allocate in Inspector to conduct an inspection for hydraulic test of boiler &amp; others.</li>\n	<li>After satisfactory result of hydraulic test of boiler, operation certificate (Form-VI) will be issued for next 12 months from the date of hydraulic test.</li>\n	<li>The entrepreneur can view and download the digital copy of the approval in his login.</li>\n</ul>', '<p>• On-line Form in lieu of Form B No.-1.</p>', '<p>Renewal of Boiler License: 7 days</p>');
