lign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">16000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:76px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; height:5px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">20000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:140px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; height:16px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" class=\"Default\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:12pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\"><span style=\"color:black\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\">above 1000</span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:66px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; height:16px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">4000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:66px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; height:16px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">5000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:66px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; height:16px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">6000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:47px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; height:16px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">7000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:57px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; height:16px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">8000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:57px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; height:16px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">9000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:66px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; height:16px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">20000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:76px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; height:16px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p align=\"right\" style=\"text-align:right\"><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span style=\"font-size:11.5pt\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif\">25000</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	</tbody>\n</table>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<p> </p>\n', 'Application for Registration and Grant of Factory License', '', 0, '<p><strong>Submission of Application: </strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>The Entrepreneur shall submit application on-line through <strong>SWAAGAT </strong>(https://swaagat.tripura.gov.in).</li>\n	<li>The application is pre-scrutinized online at SWAAGAT<strong> </strong>to verify that the application is in full form with all required enclosures.</li>\n	<li>The deficiencies, if any, in the application will be informed by the scrutinizing officers to the applicant.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><strong>Processing of the Application: </strong></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>If the application is found to be in order, the department will allocate an inspector to conduct an Inspection.</li>\n	<li>The inspector then uploads the inspection report to the Department.</li>\n	<li>Based on the report, if all are in order, Chief Inspector of Factories &amp; Boilers will sign and upload the approval in SWAAGAT portal.</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The entrepreneur can view and download the digital copy of the approval in his login.</p>', '<ul>\n	<li>\n	<p>• Scan copy of filled up application duly signed by the Occupier andManager with date and seal.</p>\n\n	<p>• Plan drawing of the factory and Reference Number, if any.</p>\n\n	<p>• Documents, if any changes in occupiership or land.</p>\n\n	<p>• Compliance Report on Statutory Provisions.</p>\n\n	<p>• NOC from Fire Department.</p>\n\n	<p>• Information of Boiler, if any.</p>\n\n	<p>• Such other particulars as the Chief Inspector of Factories &amp; Boilers mayrequire.</p>\n	</li>\n</ul>', '<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>Factory License: 30 days.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>');
