		</tr>\n		<tr>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:244px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:1px solid black\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\">Exceed 200</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n			<td style=\"border-bottom:1px solid black; width:244px; padding:0cm 7px 0cm 7px; border-top:none; border-right:1px solid black; border-left:none\" valign=\"top\">\n			<p><span style=\"font-size:11pt\"><span style=\"line-height:normal\"><span style=\"text-autospace:none\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Calibri&quot;,sans-serif\"><span lang=\"EN-IN\" style=\"font-family:&quot;Bookman Old Style&quot;,serif\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\">Rs. 1000.00</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n			</td>\n		</tr>\n	\n</table>\n', 'License /renewal of License under the Contract Labour ( Regulation and Abolition) Act, 1970 ', '', 0, '<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\">i). Applicant is to submit the application Form ( form – IV)  </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\">along with required documents, proof   of fee  deposited and Security Money .</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\">ii). verification of the document &amp; Spot Inspection if require.</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\">iii) After having satisfaction ,application with its enclosures will be forwarded  to the  Licensing  Authority </span></span></span