(49, '<a href=\"/node/38244\" hreflang=\"en\">Labour-Registration-Building</a>', '', 0, '<a href=\"/node/13947\" hreflang=\"en\">CFE-DOL3</a>', 'Consent for Establishment', 'Directorate of Labour', '<p><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>Fee depend upon number of workers. </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\">a) is upto 100 workers   Rs.500 /-</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\">b) exceed 100 workers but does not exceeds 500 workers  Rs.1 ,000/</span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>c) exceeds 500 workers   Rs.2,000/-</span></span></span></p>', 'Registration under the Building &amp; Other Construction Workers’ Welfare (RECS) Act, 1996 ', '', 0, '<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>i). Applicant is to submit the application Form ( form – 1) along with required documents and  proof of fee deposited</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>ii). Verification of the document &amp; Spot  Inspection if require.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>iii).After having  satisfaction ,application with its  enclosures will be    forwarded to the  Registering   Authority </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>iv) Any  dissatisfaction with application to be  communicated to the    applicant.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span