oof  of   fee deposited  </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>ii). Verification of the document &amp; Spot Inspection if  require.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>iii).After having  satisfaction ,application with its  enclosures will be   </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>  forwarded to the  Registering   Authority </span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>iv) Any dissatisfaction with application to be communicated to the    applicant.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>vi). Received corrected application submitted to Registering Authority.</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span><span>vii). Registration issued.</span></span></span></p>', '<p><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>i). Proof of fee deposited</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>ii) Voter ID/ Aadhaar Card  </span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>iii)  In case of registered under Company  Act -PAN Card copy</span></span></span></span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span><span><span><span><span lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\" xml:lang=\"EN-IN\"><span>iv) In case of partner- partnership deed</